@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #E8F4FA
skinparam classBorderColor #2C7DA0
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Processing
Processing --> Completed : submit
Completed --> Active : approve
Completed : entry / log route
Active --> Reviewed : confirm
Reviewed --> Created : cancel
Created --> Rejected : review
Created : entry / log route
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml